<emphasis italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">J.L. Newman 62</emphasis>
). Fruits edible when ripe and dry (
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="61" pageNumber="62">E.S. Macha 600</emphasis>
).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
